    "Since the policy decision is temporary, the stand itself may not be the primary concern.",
    "Rather, both teachers and students need to be aware of their university's position on it to determine their actions and know what potential consequences they may need to bear.",
    "While it is true that both HKUST and CUHK grant their staff a degree of flexibility and professional autonomy in decision-making, the technology is new to most.",
